name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 92: Eat all the raw spaghetti

content.html:
Dear Internet,On this weeks episode, we talk about being mean to robots, what to do when you fail the team building game, and working out in your backyard. We would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet.Sincerely,The coHosts- Nick, Jennifer, Michael, and Tim Lanning!Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!
